## Asset Loading Performance

### Preloading Important Assets

```erb
<!-- Preload critical CSS -->
<%= preload_link_tag "application.css" %>

<!-- Preload important images -->
<%= preload_link_tag asset_path("hero-background.jpg"), as: "image" %>

<!-- Preload fonts -->
<%= preload_link_tag asset_path("custom-font.woff2"), as: "font", type: "font/woff2", crossorigin: "anonymous" %>
```

### Lazy Loading Images

```erb
<!-- Lazy load below-the-fold images -->
<%= image_tag "large-image.jpg",
    alt: "Large image",
    loading: "lazy",
    class: "w-full h-auto" %>
```

